728143f-a.folder: Van Wyck Boulevard & Jamaica Avenue, Queens, NY
728143f-a.original_title: Queens: Van Wyck Boulevard - Jamaica Avenue
728143f-a.text:
Van Wyek Boulevard (right), at the S.E. corner of Jamaica Avenue, showing the former Distler's Hotel. John Distler settled in Jamaica in 1876 as the proprietor of the West End Hotel and the park of five acres. He was also connected with Saenger's Hotel in Jamaica.
View 2 is north toward Jamaica Avenue.

View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1922
View 2: P. L. Sperr  May 7, 1934
